"```sql\nSELECT s.School AS SchoolName, sat.AvgScrWrite AS AverageWritingScore, s.Phone AS CommunicationNumber\nFROM schools s\nJOIN satscores sat ON s.CDSCode = sat.cds\nWHERE (s.OpenDate > '1991-12-31' OR s.ClosedDate < '2000-01-01');\n```\n\nThis SQL query selects the school names, average writing scores, and phone numbers for schools that were opened after 1991 or closed before 2000. It joins the `schools` and `satscores` tables using the `CDSCode` as the foreign key."